Class RoleOverlapResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • sailpoint.tools.xml.AbstractXmlObject
      • sailpoint.object.RoleOverlapResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, sailpoint.tools.xml.PersistentXmlObject

    public class RoleOverlapResult
extends AbstractXmlObject
    Represents the results of a role overlap analysis. These will be stored inside the TaskResult for role impact analysis tasks.
